{"tid":2082802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加強邊防　印度築起「長城」抵禦北寇蠻族","createTime":"2020-06-28T10:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:02:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd31a8a7054ccf6d6a847f6940f3b2e3a5f3a3b4","tid":2082802,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"美國科羅拉多州為總部的Maxar衛星圖像公司，發布了中印邊境加萬谷（Galwan Valley）的最新衛星照片，顯示中國與印度都在加強邊境的一些建設，中國擴大了前哨站的規模，而印度則是建起了一堵牆。<br />\n<br />\n盡管雙方都強調降低在邊境的對峙局面，但是雙方還是繼續做對於己方較有利的防禦準備。<br />\n<br />\n中國表示，印度在去年8月首度將現況改變，將賈姆穆（Jammu）以及喀什米爾（Kashmir）分為兩個聯邦土地，其中部分土地是與中國有爭議的未定領土。<br />\n<br />\n6月在中印邊境發生的衝突，是兩國自從1962年以來的最大衝突，兩國邊界長達3380公里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=769199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D769199&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c98d5733\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D769199&h=17e7415a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=769199</a>"},{"pid":"38fc8561591b72f2948841ffc2413f113e454914","tid":2082802,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0f9cddd90467c89d63867d2c96e7101a77eea1","tid":2082802,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"北寇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ddfe8b37180512b5b36c8f6255705a00721531","tid":2082802,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"其實洗乜起城呀<br />\n美國衛星24小時直通報料去印度軍方，睇住解放軍黎食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}